{"tid":2445866,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《蘋果》召喚寫信師 以文字撐手足","createTime":"2021-03-14T03:52:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T03:52:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0418e71de764b3baccc383495b69eb5f2037af7f","tid":2445866,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T03:52:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210314/LUJ35EQEEREFLHDXYT7C6IUURQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210314%2FLUJ35EQEEREFLHDXYT7C6IUURQ%2F&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfL1zpTq0bGO0w7tnLPpoXkc%3D&h=06e3959a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210314%2FLUJ35EQEEREFLHDXYT7C6IUURQ%2F&h=ca266e91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210314/LUJ35EQEEREFLHDXYT7C6IUURQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》召喚寫信師 以文字撐手足<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MBCVAbsqHAP1gwBtib1nzJT-D1Y=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZUI7IU4Y6RDXTAGFNO6SXNKOCE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMBCVAbsqHAP1gwBtib1nzJT-D1Y%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZUI7IU4Y6RDXTAGFNO6SXNKOCE.jpg&h=8d0da637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n暴政將一場民主派初選定性「顛覆國家政權」，以國安法之名將39人推入囚室，自由無期。誠如黃之鋒親筆信所言，在牢房中跟恐懼及孤寂搏鬥絕不容易，尤其部份人被單獨囚禁，與人溝通的權利亦被剝奪。不少香港人化身「寫信師」，希望一份微小支持，超越高牆穿透鐵窗，溫暖每一位在囚者。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果日報》冀能成為連接高牆內外的窗口，誠邀讀者執筆寫信，向200名在囚手足送上你們的支持，我們挑選後每日在報章刊登，讓失去自由的手足看到你們的心意，累積力量撐下去。<br />\n<br />\n（讀者電郵請發送到letterstoprison@appledaily.com或來函將軍澳工業邨駿盈街8號《蘋果日報》編輯部）<br />\n<br />\n一格照片，一個故事，Follow蘋果Instagram！<br />\n<img src=\"https://arc-static.appledaily.com/hk/facebook-banner/appledaily_mobile_375x60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Farc-static.appledaily.com%2Fhk%2Ffacebook-banner%2Fappledaily_mobile_375x60.jpg&h=bfb5d27d&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}